platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Explore a beautiful handmade city in this stunning puzzler.
A handcrafted puzzle adventure with real charm.
Explore a vivid world filled with remarkable style and attention to detail.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: State of Plays brilliant adventure game lets you journey through a spellbinding paper world that has to be seen to be believed. Created in a complex process thats part origami and part stop motion, Lumino Citys highly polished environments come to life like nothing youve ever seen. But its not just the backdrops that captivatethis unique point-and-click adventure melds clever puzzles with a heartwarming story to powerful effect.
